[section#over.match.ref
    [:en] Initialization by conversion function for direct reference binding
    [:zh_CN] 直接引用绑定中通过转换函数进行初始化

[%[:en] overloading[!resolution[!initialization]]
  [:zh_CN] 重载[!～决议[!初始化]] ]
]

[para]
[:en]
Under the conditions specified in [#dcl.init.ref], a reference can be bound
directly to the result of applying a conversion function to an initializer
expression.
[:zh_CN]
在 [#dcl.init.ref] 中指定的条件下，引用可以被直接绑定到对初始化式表达式应用转换
函数的结果上。

[:en]
Overload resolution is used to select the conversion function to be invoked.
[:zh_CN]
使用重载决议来选择所要调用的转换函数。

[:en]
Assuming that [=lq]reference to [=cv cv1] [`T][=rq] is the type of the reference
being initialized, the candidate functions are selected as follows:
[:zh_CN]
假定“[=cv cv1] [`T] 的引用”为所初始化的引用，候选函数选择如下：

[list]
[item]
[:en]
Let [$R] be a set of types including
[:zh_CN]
对于任意 [`T2]，令 [$R] 为包含
[list]
[item]
[:en@~] [=lq]lvalue reference to [=cv cv2] [`T2][=rq] (when initializing an
lvalue reference or an rvalue reference to function) and
[:zh_CN@~] “[=cv cv2] [`T2] 的左值引用”（当对左值引用或函数的右值引用进行初始化
时），和
[item]
[:en@~] [=lq][=cv cv2] [`T2][=rq] and [=lq]rvalue reference to [=cv cv2] [`T2][=rq]
(when initializing an rvalue reference or an lvalue reference to function)
[:zh_CN@~] “[=cv cv2] [`T2]”和“[=cv cv2] [`T2] 的右值引用”（当对右值引用或函数的
左值引用进行初始化时）
[list:end]
[:en@~] for any [`T2].
[:zh_CN@~] 的类型集合。

[:en]
The permissible types for non-explicit conversion functions are the members of
[$R] where [=lq][=cv cv1] [`T][=rq] is reference-compatible ([#dcl.init.ref])
with [=lq][=cv cv2] [`T2][=rq].
[:zh_CN]
针对非显式转换函数的允许类型为 [$R] 的成员，其中“[=cv cv1] [`T]”与
“[=cv cv2] [`T2]”引用兼容（[#dcl.init.ref]）。

[:en]
For direct-initialization, the permissible types for explicit conversion
functions are the members of [$R] where [`T2] can be converted to type [`T] with
a (possibly trivial) qualification conversion ([#conv.qual]); otherwise there
are none.
[:zh_CN]
对于直接初始化，针对显式转换函数的允许类型为 [$R] 的成员，其中 [`T2] 可经由
（可能平凡的）限定转换（[#conv.qual]）转换为类型 [`T]；否则没有允许类型。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en]
The argument list has one argument, which is the initializer expression.
[:zh_CN]
实参列表有一个实参，就是其初始化式表达式。

[begin:note]
[:en]
This argument will be compared against the implicit object parameter of the
conversion functions.
[:zh_CN]
此实参将与转换函数的隐含对象形参进行比较。
[end:note]
